# given data and converting to SI units

ambient_pres = 99221.19 # 29.3 in Hg
ambient_temp = 26 # celsius
ambient_dens = 1.15546 # kg / m^3
velocity_corr = 0.98
chord = 0.15
span = 0.355
area_ratio = 0.1308
nozzle_pres = 497.68

velocity = velocity_corr * math.sqrt((2*nozzle_pres/ambient_dens)/(1 - area_ratio))

alphas = [2*x for x in range(10)]

# data_set = [lift_data, drag_data, moment_data]
clean_data = [
    [lb*4.4482216153 for lb in [0, 0.7, 1.5, 1.9, 2.4, 2.8, 3.1, 3.5, 3.3, 3.2]],
    [lb*4.4482216153 for lb in [-0.3, -0.3, -0.3, -0.4, -0.5, -0.5, -0.7, -1.1, -1.5, -1.7]],
    [lb*0.11298482933333 for lb in [0.3, 0.5, 0.7, 0.9, 0.8, 0., 0.8, -0.4, -1.7, -1.7]]

]

slats_data = [
    [lb*4.4482216153 for lb in [-0.2, 0.3, 1, 1.6, 2.2, 2.8, 3.4, 4, 4.1, 5.5]],
    [lb*4.4482216153 for lb in [-0.3, -0.4, -0.4, -0.4, -0.5, -0.5, -0.7, -0.8, -1.1, -1.3]],
    [lb*0.11298482933333 for lb in [-0.5, -0.2, 0, 0.1, 0.1, 0.1, 0.2, 0.2, -0.05, -0.5]]
]

flsl_data = [
    [lb*4.4482216153 for lb in [ 2.8, 3.6, 4.4, 4.8, 5.8, 6.8, 7.8, 8.8, 9.8, 10.4]],
    [lb*4.4482216153 for lb in [-0.9, -1.1, -1.3, -1.5, -1.7, -2, -2.2, -2.5, -2.8, -3.2]],
    [lb*0.11298482933333 for lb in [-6.3, -6.6, -6.9, -7.2, -7.4, -7.8, -8, -8.3, -8.6, -9]]
]

flaps_data = [
    [lb*4.4482216153 for lb in [3.1, 3.9, 4.8, 5.5, 6.5, 7.3, 8.1, 8.7, 8.8, 7.8]],
    [lb*4.4482216153 for lb in [-0.9, -1.1, -1.3, -1.5, -1.7, -2, -2.3, -2.8, -3.3, -3.9]],
    [lb*0.11298482933333 for lb in [-5.6, -5.8, -6.2, -6.6, -7.1, -7.5, -8.2, -9.5, -10.7, -11.5]]
]

data = [
    clean_data, slats_data, flsl_data, flaps_data
]
In [3]:
# finding coefficients
lift_coefficients = [
    [lift / (0.5 * ambient_dens * (velocity**2) * chord * span) for lift in data_set[0]] for data_set in data
]

drag_coefficients = [
    [-drag / (0.5 * ambient_dens * (velocity**2) * chord * span) for drag in data_set[1]] for data_set in data
]

moment_coefficients = [
    [moment / (0.5 * ambient_dens * (velocity**2) * (chord**2) * span) for moment in data_set[2]] for data_set in data
]

]

In [55]:
moment_lift = [[], [], [], []]

for i in range(4):
    for j in range(10):
        if le_moment_coefficients[i][j] == 0 or lift_coefficients[i][j] == 0:
            ml = 0
        else:
            ml = le_moment_coefficients[i][j] / lift_coefficients[i][j] 

        moment_lift[i].append(ml)
        
plt.figure(dpi=230, figsize=(5,5))
plt.style.use(['science', 'no-latex'])

plt.plot(alphas, moment_lift[0], label='Clean')
plt.plot(alphas, moment_lift[1], label='Slats', marker='.')
plt.plot(alphas, moment_lift[2], label='Flaps and Slats', marker='^')
plt.plot(alphas, moment_lift[3], label='Flaps', marker='s')

plt.grid(linestyle='--', linewidth=0.2)
plt.legend()
plt.xlabel('$\\alpha$')
plt.xticks(alphas)
plt.ylabel('$C_{M,LE} / C_L$')
plt.show()
In [27]:
center_pressures = [[], [], [], []]
for j in range(4):
    for i in range(len(lift_coefficients[0])):
        c_n = (lift_coefficients[j][i] * math.cos(math.radians(alphas[i])) + drag_coefficients[j][i]*math.sin(math.radians(alphas[j])))/(math.cos(math.radians(alphas[i]))**2 - math.sin(math.radians(alphas[i]))**2)
        
        if c_n == 0:
            c_cp = 0.25
        else:
            c_cp = 0.25 - (moment_coefficients[j][i]/c_n)
            
        center_pressures[j].append(c_cp*chord)
        
plt.figure(dpi=230, figsize=(5,5))
plt.style.use(['science', 'no-latex'])

plt.plot(alphas, center_pressures[0], label='Clean')
plt.plot(alphas, center_pressures[1], label='Slats', marker='.')
plt.plot(alphas, center_pressures[2], label='Flaps and Slats', marker='^')
plt.plot(alphas, center_pressures[3], label='Flaps', marker='s')

plt.grid(linestyle='--', linewidth=0.2)
plt.legend()
plt.xlabel('$\\alpha$')
plt.xticks(alphas)
plt.ylabel('$x_{cp}$ [m]')
plt.show()
